This is the README file for the MC-SYM core library.

For instructions on how to install the core package see the INSTALL file.
For a release history, new features and bug-fix notes see the NEWS file.

The Manual is available in postscript and pdf version under the name
Manual.ps and Manual.pdf in the docs directory.

You may either contact us via our web page http://www-lbit.iro.umontreal.ca
or via email mcsym@iro.umontreal.ca


MAILING LIST:

